file: crates/ctx-summarize/Cargo.toml
behavior: Package manifest for ctx-summarize, a binary+library crate that runs leaf-up context-tree summarization as a thin shell over prompt files and a pluggable agent.
edit_notes:
  - Binary (src/main.rs) and library (src/lib.rs) targets are both named explicitly; lib is ctx_summarize, bin is ctx-summarize.
  - Depends on ctx-core via relative path "../ctx-core"; must stay in the same workspace layout.
  - Lints are inherited from workspace ([lints] workspace = true), not defined locally.
functions:
invariants:
external_deps:
  - ignore: crate for walking the source tree while respecting .gitignore-style excludes, used to build the leaf/context tree.